\[
1 + 2^x + 2 \cdot 2^{2x} = y^2
\]

This can be further simplified to:

\[
1 + 2^x + 2^{2x+1} = 1 + 2^x + 2 \cdot (2^x)^2 = 1 + 2^x + 2 \cdot 2^{2x} = 1 + 2^x + 2^{2x+1} = 1 + 2^x + 2^{2x} \cdot 2 = 1 + 2^x + 2^{2x} \cdot 2 = 1 + 2^x + 4 \cdot 2^{2x}
\]

